quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  46,29,aur jab hum ne junoo mein se kayi shakhs tumhari taraf mutwajjah kiye ke quran sunen. to jab woh is ke paas aeye to ( aapas mein ) kehnay lagey ke khamosh raho. jab ( parhna ) tamam howa to apni baradri ke logon mein wapas gay ke ( un ko ) nasiyaat karen
  46,30,kehnay lagey ke ae qoum! hum ne aik kitaab suni hai jo moose ke baad nazil hui hai. jo ( kitaaben ) is se pehlay ( nazil hui ) hain un ki tasdeeq karti hai ( aur ) sacha ( deen ) aur seedha rasta batati hai
  46,31,ae qoum! khuda ki taraf bulanay walay ki baat qubool karo aur is par imaan lao. khuda tumahray gunah bakhash day ga aur tumhe dukh dainay walay azaab se panah mein rakhay ga
  46,32,aur jo shakhs khuda ki taraf bulanay walay ki baat qubool nah kere ga to woh zameen mein ( khuda ko ) aajiz nahi kar sakay ga aur nah is ke siwa is ke himayati hon ge. yeh log Sarih gumraahi mein hain
  46,33,kiya unhon ne nahi samgha ke jis khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko pedakiya aur un ke peda karne se thaka nahi. woh is ( baat ) par bhi Qadir hai ke mardon ko zindah kar day. haan haan woh har cheez par Qadir hai
  46,34,aur jis roz aag ke samnay kiye jayen ge ( aur kaha jaye ga )kiya yeh haq nahi hai? to kahin ge kyun nahi hamaray perwar-digaar ki qasam ( haq hai ) hukum hoga ke tum jo ( duniya mein ) inkaarkiya karte they ( ab ) azaab ke mazay chako
  46,35,pas ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jis terhan aur aliiiii himmat paighambar sabr karte rahay hain isi terhan tum bhi sabr karo aur un ke liye ( azaab ) jaldi nah mango. jis din yeh is cheez ko dekhen ge jis ka un se wadakiya jata hai to ( khayaal karen ge ke ) goya ( duniya mein ) rahay hi nah they magar gharri bhar din. ( yeh quran ) pegham hai. so ( ab ) wohi halaak hon ge jo nafarman they
